Implementation Notes:
- Levenshtein distance for command suggestions (Git-style)
- Guards are composable functions on Conjecture
- Version info injected via ldflags at build time
- Per-command help with -h/--help
- Global flags: -v (version), -V (verbose), -h (help)
- Errors to stderr, output to stdout
- Exit codes: 0 success, 1 error

Testing:
- Manual integration test via make test-integration
- Guard violations tested for all state transitions

Deviations:
- Used --hypothesis instead of -h for add command to avoid
  conflict with help flag (noted in help text)
